Vendored minimum inference subset of RangiLyu/nanodet (Apache-2.0).
Source: https://github.com/RangiLyu/nanodet
See LICENSE for the upstream license terms.

Training, evaluation, and optimizer components are intentionally
omitted — only the dependencies required for inference (build_model,
Pipeline, check_point.load_model_weight, util.config.load_config,
batch_process.stack_batch_img, collate.naive_collate, repvgg convert)
are included.
